room_title: Escape room "The Roswell Incident" by Portsmouth Escape Room in Portsmouth
room_description:
It's July 1947. The UFO crash has the reporters more interested than ever. Your contact in Roswell Air Force Base has given you access to a top secret area in the facility for you to find the truth about the incident.
You and a select group of reporters have infiltrated the base and have exactly one hour to find extraterrestrial life evidence before the guards are back.
